title.rendered: Taj777 news has been partnered with Satte Pe Satta T10 Cricket League

content.rendered:
Satte Pe Satta is a T10 Cricket League. This league Contain 5 Tournaments & 75 Matches. The League Started from 16 August 2023 to 16 September 2023. There are 8 teams in season 1 & season 2.

Taj777 news has been partnered with “Satte Pe Satta” T10 Cricket League. We are happy to announce that we are proud sponsor of team “Khatron Ke Khiladi”.

Satte Pe Satta Season 1 Match Schedule:

MATCH 1 – GROUP B

WESTERN WARRIORS vs CRUSHING CHAMPIONS

16 AUG – 6 PM

MATCH 2 – GROUP B

GIFTED GANGSTERS vs HUNDRED HITTERS

16 AUG – 8 PM

MATCH 3 – GROUP A

KRAZY KILLES vs POWERFUL PANDAS

16 AUG – 10 PM

MATCH 4 – GROUP A

POWERFUL PANDAS vs THUNDERBOLT TITANS

17 AUG – 6 PM

MATCH 5 – GROUP B

WESTERN WARRIORS vs GIFTED GANGSTERS

17 AUG – 8 PM

MATCH 6 – GROUP A

KRAZY KILLES vs MAJESTIC MAHARAJAHS

17 AUG – 10 PM

MATCH 7 – GROUP B

CRUSHING CHAMPIONS vs GIFTED GANGSTERS

18 AUG – 6 PM

MATCH 8 – GROUP B

WESTERN WARRIORS vs HUNDRED HITTERS

18 AUG – 8 PM

MATCH 9 – GROUP A

MAJESTIC MAHARAJAHS vs THUNDERBOLT TITANS

18 AUG – 10 PM

MATCH 10 – GROUP A

KRAZY KILLES VS THUNDERBOLT TITANS

19 AUG – 6 PM

MATCH 11 – GROUP B

CRUSHING CHAMPIONS vs HUNDRED HITTERS

19 AUG – 8 PM

MATCH 12 – GROUP A

MAJESTIC MAHARAJAHS vs POWERFUL PANDAS

19 AUG – 10 PM

MATCH 13 – SF 1

GROUP A 1ST PLACE vs GROUP B 2ND PLACE

20 AUG – 6 PM

MATCH 14 – SF 2

GROUP A 2ND PLACE vs GROUP B 1ST PLACE

20 AUG – 8 PM

MATCH 15 – FINAL

WINNER OF SF 1 vs WINNER OF SF 2

20 AUG – 10 PM

Satte Pe Satta now Live on You Tube

View all matches on https://www.youtube.com/@iwe2314
